{"type":"text","timestamp":1775866521049,"sessionID":"ses_2861f8d58ffeA2I83Wpw4C47Gn","part":{"id":"prt_d79e4a290001dXw7DtncCbK8mo","messageID":"msg_d79e487900016CoBV2J8mR95sE","sessionID":"ses_2861f8d58ffeA2I83Wpw4C47Gn","type":"text","text":"I see there's an existing proposal for AR-012. Let me update it to AR-013 — Redis Storage Implementation as specified in the requirements:","time":{"start":1775866521046,"end":1775866521046}}}
